{"tid":913176,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"發達大計","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:30:47.000Z","uid":175032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7897131f71ce75951629d891a3079fb07818cf41","tid":913176,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cuhkibd.org/stoolbank\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuhkibd.org%2Fstoolbank&d=dd8wLIf4IWT4QyqTJqm3%2BFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6a90bdd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cuhkibd.org/stoolbank</a><br />\n<br />\n腸道微生物的原材料是健康人士的大便，因此你的大便樣本是十分寶貴的！您只需要慷慨持續地捐贈大便, 就能幫助很多病人。<br />\n<br />\n為確保FMT安全，大便捐贈者需要符合嚴謹的捐贈標準。我們會為您進行一些簡單的面試和化驗您的生物樣本。如果您通過測試並可以經常來威爾斯親王醫院捐贈大便，便能成為合資格的捐贈者。<br />\n<br />\n捐贈者可於每次捐助獲得100元現金作為交通津貼。有興趣人士請填寫以下表格!　<br />\n<br />\n你所提供的資料會用於有關香港中文大學腸道微生物研究，亦作日後聯絡之用，只有獲本部門授權人員方可查閱。如有任何查詢，或於遞交表格後欲更正或查詢個人資料的使用，歡迎於辦公時間內致電 26373225 聯絡我們。"},{"pid":"f085e684138f3a07a3d8d4fcdf306dadfca79635","tid":913176,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"一日可捐幾多次"},{"pid":"be6ea437efdfc9c0a0c2def116a7084116c48a52","tid":913176,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f085e684138f3a07a3d8d4fcdf306dadfca79635","tid":913176,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"一日可捐幾多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"有到叫你tick星期一至五每日一次"},{"pid":"c51bd0eb29570aced264efa3564d47d746d4eb14","tid":913176,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"柯一次分幾次捐<br />\nFatfat"},{"pid":"01bea614fad49c785687811cba65cc8e15634318","tid":913176,"uid":79317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"100蚊一令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2398353b02807e3e08193fd5f1cd597393723c9","tid":913176,